name: Texas A&M PAWS
description: Our mission is to raise awareness and donate to our philanthropy, International Animal Rescue, while upholding the core values of Texas A&M University. Alongside our philanthropy, we will be doing many service projects dealing with the rescuing and rehabilitating of animals around Texas. These include, but are not limited to, common household pets, rodents, woodland creatures, etc. As an organization, we value every animal no matter how big or small. Through this organization, we aim to provide a strong sisterhood for which our girls will be able to grow as both leaders and as role models.
summary: Our mission is to raise awareness and donate to our philanthropy, International Animal Rescue, while upholding the core values of Texas A&M University.
